00:36:24.480 --> 00:36:25.000
is crying.

00:36:25.000 --> 00:36:26.320
He's having surgery tomorrow.

00:36:26.320 --> 00:36:27.639
We'll take good care of him.

00:36:28.519 --> 00:36:29.119
Hurry up.

00:36:33.599 --> 00:36:34.199
Hurry up.

00:36:34.719 --> 00:36:35.360
Okay.

00:36:35.679 --> 00:36:36.760
I'll grab my stuff.

00:36:36.800 --> 00:36:37.599
Grab my stuff.

00:36:37.599 --> 00:36:38.176
Okay.

00:36:42.840 --> 00:36:43.440
Hurry up.

00:36:45.480 --> 00:36:46.440
- Open the door.
- Get out of the car.

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:47.360
Turn off the engine.

00:36:47.920 --> 00:36:48.679
Don't run.

00:36:48.960 --> 00:36:50.159
It'd worsen the case.

00:37:07.239 --> 00:37:08.199
Liu Yi.

00:37:08.199 --> 00:37:09.679
Don't cry. Dad is here.

00:37:09.679 --> 00:37:10.360
It's okay.

00:37:10.360 --> 00:37:11.159
Good boy. It's okay.

00:37:11.880 --> 00:37:12.840
Don't cry anymore.

00:37:13.152 --> 00:37:15.840
You're having surgery tomorrow.
Your heart can't take it.

00:37:18.880 --> 00:37:19.840
Why would I run?

00:37:21.119 --> 00:37:22.239
I sell bootleg tapes.

00:37:22.960 --> 00:37:24.119
I'll go to the police station

00:37:24.440 --> 00:37:25.800
and explain everything.

00:37:27.280 --> 00:37:28.800
Liu Yi, stop crying.

00:37:28.800 --> 00:37:30.800
Look, I am pulling over now.

00:37:32.280 --> 00:37:33.719
I'll go to the police station

00:37:33.719 --> 00:37:34.760
and explain everything.

00:37:42.599 --> 00:37:53.639
♪So bitter♪

00:39:09.199 --> 00:39:10.440
Wait for you to come back.

00:39:11.840 --> 00:39:13.079
After our kid has surgery,

00:39:14.840 --> 00:39:15.639
our whole family

00:39:16.920 --> 00:39:18.159
will visit Jiuyangou.

00:40:15.199 --> 00:40:15.960
Qin'e!

00:40:16.320 --> 00:40:17.679
Qin'e, terrible! Qin'e!

00:40:18.559 --> 00:40:19.360
Qin'e!

00:40:19.760 --> 00:40:20.559
Qin'e!

00:40:24.199 --> 00:40:24.800
What's wrong?

00:40:25.480 --> 00:40:26.559
Yu, don't move around!

00:40:28.119 --> 00:40:28.920
Qin'e!

00:40:29.480 --> 00:40:31.239
Take this down, hurry!

00:40:31.392 --> 00:40:32.039
Qin'e!

00:40:32.039 --> 00:40:32.559
Hurry!

00:40:32.920 --> 00:40:33.840
Rescue her first!

00:40:34.280 --> 00:40:36.320
Get down! Don't gather here.

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:37.079
Hurry, get down!

00:40:37.079 --> 00:40:38.599
Slow down, be careful!

00:40:38.880 --> 00:40:39.639
Slow down.

00:40:39.960 --> 00:40:40.559
Careful!

00:40:40.559 --> 00:40:41.920
Slow down.

00:40:41.920 --> 00:40:43.119
Come on, lend a hand.

00:40:43.280 --> 00:40:44.400
Here, catch this person.

00:40:44.400 --> 00:40:45.880
- Careful!
- Careful!

00:40:45.880 --> 00:40:46.840
Protect the legs!

00:40:46.840 --> 00:40:47.440
The head!

00:40:49.599 --> 00:40:50.760
Slow down, all of you!

00:40:50.760 --> 00:40:51.400
The legs!

00:40:51.400 --> 00:40:52.559
Watch out, don't crowd!

00:40:53.360 --> 00:40:54.119
Get a vehicle!

00:40:54.760 --> 00:40:55.920
Get a vehicle!

00:40:55.920 --> 00:40:56.440
Get help!

00:40:56.440 --> 00:40:57.400
Get help!

00:40:57.400 --> 00:40:58.079
Get a vehicle!

00:40:58.320 --> 00:40:59.159
Get a vehicle!

00:41:06.639 --> 00:41:07.400
Someone's there!

00:41:12.000 --> 00:41:13.320
Someone got hit!

00:41:14.039 --> 00:41:15.480
Hurry, go rescue him now!

00:41:15.880 --> 00:41:17.039
Hurry, rescue him!

00:41:19.000 --> 00:41:20.000
Hurry!

00:41:33.760 --> 00:41:34.559
Get a car!

00:41:43.440 --> 00:41:44.840
Someone, help!

00:41:44.840 --> 00:41:46.079
There are kids below!

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:47.119
Master Song.

00:41:49.920 --> 00:41:51.079
Come here, get out!

00:41:51.239 --> 00:41:52.400
Hurry. Come on!

00:41:53.840 --> 00:41:55.079
Come on!

00:41:55.800 --> 00:41:57.152
Come out, get over here!

00:41:58.000 --> 00:41:59.239
Come over here, follow me!

00:41:59.719 --> 00:42:00.639
Catch this!

00:42:00.639 --> 00:42:01.280
Get moving!

00:42:28.800 --> 00:42:29.400
What happened?

00:42:29.800 --> 00:42:30.480
What's wrong?

00:43:05.184 --> 00:43:06.880
(Preview)

00:43:09.061 --> 00:43:10.421
She doesn't sing anymore.

00:43:10.501 --> 00:43:11.262
She stopped singing?

00:43:11.262 --> 00:43:14.021
After that stage collapse,
she couldn't sing anymore.

00:43:14.141 --> 00:43:15.021
Faster.

00:43:15.021 --> 00:43:15.822
Time's tight.

00:43:15.822 --> 00:43:17.182
Don't make the stitches too tight.

00:43:17.182 --> 00:43:19.941
Leave the performers and the play
some breathing room.

00:43:19.941 --> 00:43:21.501
Pay me back now.

00:43:21.501 --> 00:43:23.141
I need the money to turn things around.

00:43:23.302 --> 00:43:24.342
Xue Guisheng

00:43:24.822 --> 00:43:26.342
wanted to pursue Qin'e.

00:43:26.662 --> 00:43:28.222
Xue Guisheng wanted to pursue Qin'e?

00:43:28.501 --> 00:43:29.702
What happened in the troupe?

00:43:29.702 --> 00:43:31.822
This is a society ruled by law.
Abide by the law.

00:43:31.822 --> 00:43:32.782
Don't fight.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪